116  inline bool setParent(ContainerBase* parent) {
117  if (parent_) {
118  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Tried to add stage '" << name() << "' to two parents");
119  return false; // it's not allowed to add a stage to a parent if it already has one
120  }
121  parent_ = parent;
122  return true;
123  }

279 class ConnectingPrivate : public ComputeBasePrivate
280 {

282 
283  using StatePair = std::pair<Interface::const_iterator, Interface::const_iterator>;
284  struct StatePairLess
285  {
286  bool operator()(const StatePair& x, const StatePair& y) const {
287  return x.first->priority() + x.second->priority() < y.first->priority() + y.second->priority();
288  }
289  };
290 
291  template <Interface::Direction other>
292  inline StatePair make_pair(Interface::const_iterator first, Interface::const_iterator second);
293 
294 public:
295  inline ConnectingPrivate(Connecting* me, const std::string& name);
296 
297  InterfaceFlags requiredInterface() const override;
298  bool canCompute() const override;
299  void compute() override;
300

305 
306  // ordered list of pending state pairs
307  ordered<StatePair, StatePairLess> pending;
